  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced", 
    "date": "2001-06-27", 
    "text": "Energy Market Monitoring Act - Amends the Department of Energy Organization Act to: (1) direct the Comptroller General to monitor and evaluate the functions and activities of the Federal Energy Regulatory Commission (FERC); and (2) subject to the Comptroller's jurisdiction any owner or operator of facilities or business premises subject to FERC jurisdiction . Grants the Comptroller General enforcement powers."
